title: New: Mannequins on 7th Street â€“ In Two
content:
Belgium via London duo Mannequins on 7th Street cropped up towards the end of last summer with their intoxicating brand of smooth electronic-pop, and have spent the last six months or so refining their sound.

New release, In Two, is another sleek, fragile number, showcasing their dense, diverse sound, alongside their ability to pen a killer chorus. Check out In Two below, lifted from an EP out in September.
